  <h1>About wagetheftcalc.com</h1>
  <p>wagetheftcalc.com is a free employment law / wage and hour resource maintained by The Click Lab. Our calculator and guides help people understand wage theft and unpaid wage recovery and what factors affect outcomes.</p>
  <h2>What we do</h2><p>We translate complex legal and financial concepts into plain-English calculators. Every page is reviewed by our <a href="/editorial">editorial team</a>.</p>
  <h2>What we don&rsquo;t do</h2><p>We don&rsquo;t provide legal or professional advice. For your specific situation, consult a licensed professional.</p>
  <h2>How we make money</h2><p>Display advertising via Google AdSense. We don&rsquo;t sell reader data. See <a href="/privacy">privacy policy</a>.</p>
  <h2>Contact</h2><p>See our <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
</BaseLayout>
